data.description: Check out this beautifully updated 3-bedroom colonial nestled away in Hamburg Township.  Minutes from the Lakeland Trail, for walking and biking. No HOA. Enjoy the hardwood floors, gas fireplace and 1st floor laundry. Upstairs you will find three large bedrooms and a full bath with direct access from the primary bedroom. Enjoy extra storage in the concrete crawl space with direct access from your kitchen. Entertain on the large deck that overlooks your fire pit; back yard is fully fenced. Home is wired for a whole house generator.
